desc: Point to point race with the criss-crossing up the wazoo that features a lot of original sections & new stunt elements such as, the first moving ramps in GTA & a bunch of other cool stuff. ''Agile bikes'' perform the best, however if u decide to pick Faggio, it's probably time to face the cruel reality - you are a damn idiot and ur mom is lying to you when she says that you are a bright kid, don't listen to her.    Word Record - 02.57 by Asudora.
creator: -Hitokiri-
name: HIT Fastest Bike Parkour

desc: Slalom in between the shipping containers and find the perfect line through the decreasing radius left turn to carry the most speed into the chicane. GP (Grand prix) style race made using cunning stunts props that can also be a drift circuit with muscles in rain. [ Press L1 at the end if you want to Bookmark. ]
name: Dockyard Autocross
creator: opalescentfalcon

desc: GP (Grand prix) style race made with cunning stunts props. This circuit has many elevation changes and two technical chicanes. Enjoy the roar of your engine when blasting through the tunnel. [ Press L1 at the end if you want to bookmark.]
creator: opalescentfalcon
name: Tunnel Run

desc: Super Stunt Sky. O céu de Los Santos tem mais do que poluição e aviões com pilotos maluco, e você vai ver isso nessa corrida. Thanks for the 700lk likes and 1.8m played
name: ' # Super Stunt Sky #
creator: Guilherme_94

desc: Every single bike works. Non-contact mode is preferred, but not necessary. Get ready for the jumps, tubes, wall rides, trenches, sharp turns, tight ropes, obstacle lines, & water crossing. But If you manage to go through all this hell before ur opponents then you'll have a privilege to say to them, ''Get on my level'' and this time it will make literal sense... Features the 1st bike elevator in GTA. GTA mode is available.
creator: -Hitokiri-
name: HIT - Get On My Level

desc: Rainbowlândia, corrida com todas as cores. @ Osiris - T20 - Zentorno - XF - Nero - XA-21 - Visionare.
name: ' # Rainbowland
creator: Guilherme_94

desc: Tron bike (Shotaro) performs the best, plus if you don't pick a Tron bike in a race that is called ''TRON'', why in the hell did you buy the most expensive bike in the game! Since it's a Tron themed race it's supposed to be played at night, so don't touch anything, if i set it at night you play it at night, i don't give a damn! Features new stunt elements such as; a double boosted lane & wall phasing.
creator: -Hitokiri-
name: HIT - T R O N

desc: Rocket down Raton Canyon and enjoy the views from the climb up Mount Josiah, before an unforgettable final stretch.
name: Love Canyon
creator: EdwardT_RSN_CC

desc: Stunt racing built in the city for sports and supercars. Turn-based with a length of 6.55km.
creator: abconstruction
name: Stunt - Flying Circus

desc: Drive a stunt race with different angled wallrides and jumps in a crossing track at a height level of approximately 500m.
name: Stunt - Wallride 40°-90°
creator: abconstruction

desc: Recent researches proved that city center buildings have been infested with strange pinkish objects. Oh no.
creator: mathilya
name: Pink Panther

desc: Get into this stunt race in the city including jumps, a big ramp, house climbing, loops and wallrides on various raceways. Turn-based with a length of 6.67km.
name: Stunt - Schlonberg Sachs
creator: abconstruction

desc: Turn-based with a length of 10km.
creator: abconstruction
name: Stunt - Chiliad To Ocean

desc: This race requires quick reflexes and fast car. No slow corners. Sometimes, when your car slips and you have no traction, only way to survive is to push the throttle button... let's see how brave you are
name: Fast Paced Race
creator: mathilya

desc: Stunt racing above the Alamo Sea also for Open Wheel cars. Turn-based with a length of 5.62km.
creator: abconstruction
name: Stunt - BlueRedWhite

desc: Make a stunt race over the ocean near the Raton Canyon with wallrides, jumps and a little offroad session. It´s turn-based with crossing track parts and has a length of 7km.
name: Stunt - Raton´s Cross
creator: abconstruction

desc: Starting at the Casino this race contains jumps, 2.5 loops and different raceways like tube, raceway and highway. Turn-based with a length of 7.47km, laptime ca. 3.00min.
creator: abconstruction
name: Stunt - Casino Challenge

desc: Mount Chiliad has inspired artists, hippies and death cults for generations, but until now it's offered precious little for the key Los Santos demographic: reckless supercar enthusiasts. All that changes with this towering stunt race over the iconic peak of San Andreas.
name: Stunt - Chiliad
creator: JoshuaB_RSN_CC

desc: There's a fine line between an epic descent and falling uncontrollably out of the sky, and which side you're on is going to depend on talent, judgement and just how hard the other guy is trying to kill you. Classic point to point stunt race for super cars.
creator: harrymorg3_rsn
name: Stunt - Plummet

desc: Halfway through yet another corkscrew above Downtown LS, unable to see anything more than the next 10 feet of track, struggling not to black out, you might find yourself wondering what life choices led you to this point. Because whatever they are, they were clearly excellent. Stunt race for super cars.
name: Stunt - Downtown Loop
creator: ChrisD_RSNNGCC

desc: White water rafting is for eco-liberals and cowards. Get to know the real Raton Canyon as you plunge through this relentless Stunt Race for super cars with up to fifteen other nature lovers.
creator: RSNPaulSNG
name: Stunt - Canyon Crossing

desc: You can never have too much of a good thing, especially when that thing is a gravity-defying loop-the-loop over Fort Zancudo. Kiss your already fragile grip on the laws of physics goodbye on this intense stunt race for super cars.
name: Stunt - Double Loop
creator: ChrisB_RSN_CC

desc: No, it's not a side effect of your IBS meds, you really are getting tunnel vision, and it's because you're moving at incredible speed through a ten-story tunnel in the middle of nowhere. Self-explanatory stunt race for bikes.
creator: harrymorg3_rsn
name: Stunt - Trench I

desc: When the next planeload of tourists flies into San Andreas, what do you want their first impression to be? The natural drama of cliffs, mountains and ocean? Or you and a bunch of nutjobs driving supercars around a giant wall in the middle of the sea? Thought so.
name: Stunt - East Coast
creator: ChrisD_RSNNGCC

desc: Time to wave to all your friends at the FIB as you get some turbo-charged air time over their HQ. Bonus points if you moon an informant out the passenger window. Stunt race for sports cars over the heart of the city.
creator: ChrisB_RSN_CC
name: Stunt - City Air

desc: As ever in the Golden State, you've got two choices: use every dirty trick in the book to cling to the high life, or duke it out with all the other schmucks in the gutter. You should have gotten good at this by now. Stunt race on two levels for bikes.
name: Stunt - Over and Under
creator: ChrisB_RSN_CC

desc: Back on the starting grid you were still a child. By the end of the first descent you were already a man - or possibly a woman, it's hard to tell. By the time you cross the finish line you are, to all intents and purposes, dead. In between, gravity and madness did their work as only a San Andreas stunt race can guarantee. Point to point for sports cars.
name: Stunt - Big Drop
creator: Lindo_RSN_CC

desc: Sure, exploding cars and the screams of the dying can be a little distracting. And that six pack of 48hr energy shots you nailed earlier ain't helping. But keeping your focus is your only chance on this tight and technical stunt race for bikes through every level of Los Santos.
creator: RSNPaulSNG
name: Stunt - Threading the Needle

desc: Who hasn't stood in the heart of Los Santos and looked up, past the tops of the skyscrapers, through the blanket of smog, deep into the rapidly deteriorating ozone and thought ''yes, that's an ideal starting point for a stunt race''? Don't get used to the view - you'll be down again real soon. Point to point stunt race for supercars.
name: Stunt - Plummet II
creator: harrymorg3_rsn

desc: There was a time when jumping through a wreath of flame on a poorly engineered chopper was enough to give even the most jaded patriot a semi. Those simple days are gone, but apply the same formula a thousand feet above an urban area in the middle of the night and you stand a decent chance of a sudden rush of blood to the crotch. Spectacular stunt race for bikes.
creator: ChrisD_RSNNGCC
name: Stunt - Afterburner

desc: Sure 2000cc superbikes weren't designed to spend this much time flying through the air above industrial docklands, but every step of evolutionary progress is tough on the pioneers. Jump-heavy point to point stunt race.
name: Stunt - Over the Bridge
creator: JoshuaB_RSN_CC

desc: There's nothing quite like driving through Los Santos at night. What the guide books don't tell you is that the best route is an elaborate stunt race, the best altitude is around 2000 feet, and the best vehicle is a twitchy, race-tuned motorbike. Time to break out your Snapmatic.
creator: harrymorg3_rsn
name: Stunt - Nightlife

desc: Enhanced interrogation techniques have come a long way since the early days of putting a black bag over your head and leaving you in a washer dryer for a few hours. If you're not ready to spill your guts after this stunt race for super cars over Fort Zancudo, it's probably because they're busy hosing you off the main runway.
name: Stunt - Lift Off
creator: ChrisD_RSNNGCC

desc: After a long day in the office hoping the IT guy won't check your search history, there's nothing more invigorating than the touch of the ocean breeze and the smell of salt water as it washes over a race track and floods your engine. Stunt race for sports cars. Pro tip: bring your bikini bottoms.
creator: RSNPaulSNG
name: Stunt - H200

desc: Close your eyes and get caught up in a fast-moving wave of excitement and optimism that'll take you to the very pinnacle of the banking sector. What goes up never comes crashing down. Seriously, this can only end well. Stunt race for the Sports class.
name: Stunt - Maze Bank Ascent
creator: JoshuaB_RSN_CC

desc: Two groups of crazed speed freaks take two routes around one track competing for one spot at the top of the podium. What could possibly go right? Stunt race for Muscle cars.
creator: ChrisB_RSN_CC
name: Stunt - Duel

desc: When it's not being used as the entry point for half the meth in the state, the Sandy Shores airfield is just the kind of big open space that makes you stop and ask yourself what happens when a pack of fragile sports cars charge into some 30ft bowling pins. Buckle up and watch the magic happen.
name: Stunt - Racing Alley
creator: JoshuaB_RSN_CC

desc: Time to ditch the private jet, saddle up, and learn a thing or two about corporate dominance with this stunt race for bikes through, around and over almost every skyscraper in central LS.
creator: ChrisB_RSN_CC
name: Stunt - High Flier

desc: A few massive slingshots and vertical drops around Mount Chiliad will play havoc with a full stomach. Time to skip lunch... and breakfast... and to pack a change of underwear. Point to Point stunt race for the sports class.
name: Stunt - Zebra
creator: RSNPaulSNG

desc: Any old amateur can hit top speed on their way through a fully operational wind farm. What takes really big, dumb balls is seizing every opportunity to get battered out of the sky by a stray turbine arm along the way. Off-road stunt race around RON Alternates. Helmets advised.
creator: ChrisD_RSNNGCC
name: Stunt - Turbine

desc: It's a simple formula, but it works. Keep going till you see the tops of the clouds, then turn left and head downhill for a few miles until the G-force starts to detach your skin from your bones. If you're still alive and conscious after that, well, you're pretty much on your own. Good luck. Lap race for motorcycles.
name: Stunt - 45°
creator: harrymorg3_rsn

desc: Stunt race curcuit with flat roads, tubes, jumps, and a loop. The whole track is color coded. Yellow for Left, Red for Right, Blue for Up, Green for Down, and Orange for Special.
creator: LaraCroftGTAV
name: South Side Circuit

creator: BennoAFU

creator: Bobo4211
desc: A motor racing track located in Homestead, Florida. The track, which has several configurations, has promoted several series of racing, including NASCAR, the IndyCar Series, the WeatherTech Sportscar Championship series. Restricted is for Supers, Sports(Hotring Sabre) only, and Open wheel (Dr1).
name: Homestead Miami 2.0

creator: dadslettingme
desc: Simple race with many different types of corners and straights. My first attempt to create a solid track for competitive racing. This Track is accessible with all vehicles and features various corner types with a long straight. This Track's balance leans towards Handling more than Top Speed. 1:23 average stock Feltzer time
name: SR01 - Casino Trenches

creator: crazy_man_carlos
desc: Hotwheels inspired stunt track
name: Spin cycle

creator: dastlu
desc: - Dastlu - T20 - Stay In The Middle While In The Stunt - Rate At The End ;) - Non Contact Adviced -
name: {D} Green And White

creator: dadslettingme
desc: This Track Features a large variety of corners and verticality. This Track balance leans greatly towards handling. 1:43 average stock Feltzer time.
name: SR03 - Artificial Isle

creator: dadslettingme
desc: Reversed version of Island Cruise, this track is accessible with all vehicles and features various corner types and Long straights. Track balance leans slightly towards Top Speed over Handling. Long track 1:26 average stock Feltzer time
name: SR02 - Island Cruise R
